{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/7-best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock-2/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c19973be-b031-5391-b9dc-8641c69ecbbe","excerpt":"오늘두 알고리즘 퐈이어🔥 leetcode의 30Day Challenge…","html":"<p>오늘두 알고리즘 퐈이어🔥 leetcode의 30Day Challenge는 정말 좋은것 같다. 뭘풀지를 정해주고 그렇게 까지 어렵지않은 문제들로 구성되있어서 더더욱 의지가 꺾이지 않고 달릴 수 있는 것 같다. 요즘 주식으로 핫해서 그런가 언제  <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/explore/challenge/card/30-day-leetcoding-challenge/528/week-1/3287/\">주식을 사고 판것의 이득을 구하는 문제</a>를 풀어봅시다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2\"\n        title=\"best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2\"\n        src=\"/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/e5166/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/f93b5/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 300w,\n/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/b4294/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 600w,\n/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/e5166/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 1200w,\n/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/7e26b/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 1510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"문제 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 요약</h1>\n<p>가장 이윤에 남는 방식으로만 주식을 사고 팔아서 얻은 수익을 계산해보자. <del>현실세계에서는 예측이 어려우니 절대 불가능한 일이지만 ㅋㅋ 여기서는 이윤을 다 안다는 가정하에 진행한다.</del> complexity에 대해서는 따로 추가적인 조건은 없었다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"문제 해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 해결</h1>\n<p>문제는 해결했는데 공간 복잡도 O(1), 시간 복잡도 O(n^2)으로 해결했다. O(n)으로 해결할 수 있는 방법들이 솔루션에 있었는데 해당 방법들도 다시 검토 해 볼 필요가 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-brute-force-무식한-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-brute-force-%EB%AC%B4%EC%8B%9D%ED%95%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"1 brute force 무식한 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) Brute Force <del>(무식한 방법)</del></h2>\n<p>브루트포스 알고리즘은 모는 경우의 수를 다해보는 알고리즘이다. 난 이렇게 안했다. 이렇게 하면 공간복잡도는 O(n), 시간 복잡도가 이미 O(n^n)이 되버린다. n제곱도아니고 n^n이다 ㅋㅋㅋ</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-peak-valley-approach\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-peak-valley-approach\" aria-label=\"2 peak valley approach permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2) Peak Valley Approach</h2>\n<p>난 이방법으로 해결했다.\npeak와 valley를 찾아서 그 차이를 계속 더하는 것이다.\n난 일단 순회를 하되 현재 순회중인 애가 Peak인지 확인하게 했고, valley를 가리키는 포인터(index)를 저장하여 그것의 차를 뺐다.\n그림을 보면 더욱 이해가 쉽다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2-2\"\n        title=\"best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2-2\"\n        src=\"/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/e5166/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/f93b5/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 300w,\n/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/b4294/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 600w,\n/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/e5166/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 1200w,\n/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/7e26b/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 1510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n코드는 내가 짠게 더 쉬운것 같아서 내 코드를 첨부한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>시간 복잡도 O(n), 공간복잡도 O(1)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * @param {number[]} prices\n * @return {number}\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">maxProfit</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">prices</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> minIdx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> sum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>prices<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>prices<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>minIdx<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> prices<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            minIdx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>prices<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>minIdx<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> prices<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            sum <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> prices<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>  prices<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>minIdx<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            minIdx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> sum<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"2-simple-one-pass\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-simple-one-pass\" aria-label=\"2 simple one pass permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2) Simple One Pass</h2>\n<p>이렇게 쉬운 문제였는데! 사실 세번째 풀이를 보면 이 문제는 그냥 현재보다 전것이 더 작은 것의 차의 합을 구하는 문제였다는 것을 알 수 있다.\n내가 짠 코드랑 complexity는 동일해서 큰 아쉬움은 없지만, 그래도 좀 더 크게 문제를 바라봐야겠다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2-3\"\n        title=\"best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2-3\"\n        src=\"/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/e5166/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/f93b5/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 300w,\n/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/b4294/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 600w,\n/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/e5166/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 1200w,\n/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/7e26b/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg 1510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>시간 복잡도 O(n), 공간복잡도 O(1)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>@param {number[]} prices</li>\n<li>\n<p>@return {number}\n*/\nvar maxProfit = function(prices) {\nlet sum = 0;\nfor(let i=1; i&#x3C;prices.length; i++) {\nif(prices[i] > prices[i-1]) {\nsum += prices[i] - prices[i - 1];\n}\n}\nreturn sum;\n};</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"📈 Best Time To Buy and Sell Stock 2","date":"April 06, 2020","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/d3c3df8ab029939018a3680ba821d46e/14b42/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock2.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/7-best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock-2/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/6-move-zeroes/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🙆‍♀️Move Zeroes","category":"algorithm","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/8-group-anagrams/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🏵 Group Anagrams","category":"algorithm","draft":false}}}}}